Commentary Text: Chris Morris to Kedar Jadhav, out Bowled!! How did he miss that? A slot ball but Kedar swung a tad early looking to muscle the ball over mid-wicket, the ball came after the bat passed the trajectory and crashed into middle. Was a strange dismissal. Usually you see batsmen connect those, but Tipo seems to be indicating that he slid his finger cross that one. Speedgun shows 135kph, but was that a variety slower ball? Only he will have to tell. Commentary Text: Mustafizur to Manish Pandey, out Bowled!! And the break has done it for the Royals - a soft dismissal for Manish, was the slower cutter - Mustafizur rolled his fingers across the seam, was looking to whip it through the on-side, was done in by the lack of pace, the ball richocheted onto the middle-stump off his pads. Was looking good for a big score today, but Manish's cameo has been brought to an early end. Manish Pandey b Mustafizur 31(20) [4s-3 6s-2]
